    Tenant management page.

    Lists all tenants with filtering and search capabilities.
    Supports pagination and filtering by status and search term.

    Query Parameters:
        status: Filter by tenant status (active, inactive)
        search: Search by name or slug
        page: Page number (default: 1)
        per_page: Items per page (default: 20)

    Returns:
        Rendered tenants.html template with tenant data
